1546
01:25:19,574 --> 01:25:21,492
Delirmiş bunlar.

1547
01:25:21,576 --> 01:25:22,994
Kim bu adamlar?

1548
01:25:23,077 --> 01:25:24,412
Bilmiyorum.

1549
01:25:32,422 --> 01:25:33,882
Kilidi eritti.

1550
01:25:34,924 --> 01:25:37,218
Ortaçağdan farkı yok buranın.

1551
01:25:39,597 --> 01:25:41,891
Kemoterapiler.

1552
01:25:41,932 --> 01:25:44,895
Fundoskopik muayeneler.

1553
01:25:51,110 --> 01:25:53,029
Hadi, Chekov.
Uyan artık.

1554
01:25:56,742 --> 01:25:58,327
Pavel.

1555
01:25:58,410 --> 01:25:59,870
Beni duyuyor musun?

1556
01:26:03,750 --> 01:26:05,668
