1557
01:26:07,755 --> 01:26:09,256
Pavel, konuş benimle.

1558
01:26:11,592 --> 01:26:12,885
Adın ve rütben.

1559
01:26:14,262 --> 01:26:16,181
Chekov,..

1560
01:26:16,264 --> 01:26:18,183
Pavel.

1561
01:26:18,266 --> 01:26:19,351
Rütbem...

1562
01:26:20,603 --> 01:26:22,271
